				<wikidot:authorName>Kothardarastrix</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3460794</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My pig phobia did not need this. I am simultaneously disappointed and immeasurably relieved that there is not a picture of the pig king. I'm gonna go throw up now, right after I upvote.</p> <p>On a more serious note, I can't help but think that it might be more convenient (and less HORRIBLE) to feed the never-ending entrails to non-anomalous pigs instead of Foundation personnel, since pigs are horrible, disgusting cannibals anyway. That's where I thought this was going, but what you did with it is just as AWFUL.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
