					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12286557#post-4325933</guid>
				<title>Site Criticism Team - Review</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12286557/scp-4495#post-4325933</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2019 05:26:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RockTeethMothEyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4022320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I haven't done one of these in a while. Let's get crackin'.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+[Critique]&nbsp;Click&nbsp;to&nbsp;Access</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-[Click&nbsp;to&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;Text]</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I'll admit to being a fan of anything that makes me uncomfortable, and this certainly gets there. It starts off pretty gross with a pig corpse constantly and violently spitting out its guts, and then it makes them squirm. That alone is some good imagery.</p> <p>I particularly like the sudden discovery that digestive acid destroys the intestines. It's such a fallible thing to have a weak stomach (and of course you would if pig intestines just jumped at you) and for it to lead to such a simple and straightforward resolution is fantastic. It's so gross and I <em>love it</em>.</p> <p>This was an easy +1 for me. The imagery, the human weakness, and the solution pulled this together for me.</p> <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8a9BfFSKa90">Eat like a pig</a>.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><span style="font-size:smaller;"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> <em>Opinions expressed in this review do not reflect the opinions of SCP Wiki staff as a whole. Please respond to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565328361" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span> or contact the captain of the Site Criticism Team, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565328361" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span>, for any questions or concerns relating to this review.</em></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
